  "lastUpdatedOn": "2012-05-27",
  "religion": "Stiller was brought up in a Jewish/Catholic home and he identifies with both faiths.",
  "politicalViews": "Stiller is a liberal Democrat and big contributor to the Democratic Party.",
  "author": "Tom Kershaw",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Ben Stiller was born and raised in New York City in a Jewish family of entertainers. His father is famous comedian Jerry Stiller."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Stiller's mother, Anne Meara, was raised Irish Catholic, but converted to the Jewish faith.",
      "sourceTitle": "Christina Taylor: Sweet for the holidays",
      "sourceUrl": "http://articles.mcall.com/2010-12-03/entertainment/mc-christine-taylor-20101203_1_christmas-tree-homemade-ornaments-holidays"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "As a result, Stiller considers himself both Jewish and Catholic, saying:",
      "parentId": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 4,
      "parentId": 3
    },
    {
      "parentId": 4,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I'm Jewish and Catholic. Oh yeah, a lot of guilt.",
      "sourceTitle": "Jonathan Ross interviews Owen Wilson and Ben Stiller Part 2",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U8-2ofOhJko#t=03m32s"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 5
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Stiller had a bar mitzvah, but his family celebrated both Christian and Jewish holidays growing up, though his upbringing was admittedly more Jewish.",
      "sourceTitle": "Stiller 'softy' in real life",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.jewishaz.com/jewishnews/991119/stiller.shtml"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "and now that Stiller is married to a Catholic woman, actress Christina Taylor, he is raising his family the same way.",
      "parentId": 5,
      "sourceTitle": "Christina Taylor: Sweet for the holidays",
      "sourceUrl": "http://articles.mcall.com/2010-12-03/entertainment/mc-christine-taylor-20101203_1_christmas-tree-homemade-ornaments-holidays"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 6
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Of course, the Jewish comedian has become a real-life cliche, so it wouldn't be right to not end with a bit of funny stuff. Stiller recounts performing with his father at a Jewish function:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 7
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 8,
      "parentId": 7
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "We covered 'Hey, Jude.' My father panicked, misunderstanding the lyrics and thinking our lead singer was belting out 'Hey, Jew' to a roomful of Holocaust survivors.",
      "sourceTitle": "Jews Quotes, New Jews Quotes",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.quoteidea.com/jews-quotes"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 9
    },
    {
      "parentId": 9,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Big money politics"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 10
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Stiller is a major supporter of the Democratic Party, having contributed nearly $50,000 to various Democratic candidates and causes since 2002.",
      "sourceTitle": "Ben Stiller's Federal Campaign Contribution Report",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.newsmeat.com/celebrity_political_donations/Ben_Stiller.php"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "He donated to both Hillary Clinton and Barack Obama in 2008, but forked over a whopping $25,000 to Obama, putting to shame his $4,600 to Clinton.",
      "parentId": 10
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 11
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "In 2012, Stiller expressed some disappointment in Obama's first four years, saying:"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 13,
      "parentId": 12
    },
    {
      "parentId": 13,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I'm disappointed that we haven't seen more bold decisions from him and a willingness, I think, to maybe stick to more of what he had, in his campaign, had said in terms of what he was willing to do.",
      "sourceTitle": "Ben Stiller is disappointed in Obama",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.politico.com/blogs/click/1111/Ben_Stiller_is_disappointed_in_Obama.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 14
    },
    {
      "parentId": 14,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "But in a classic \"he's better than the other guy\" moment, Stiller still showed up at a New York City party/fundraiser hosted by first lady Michelle Obama.",
      "sourceTitle": "Stars out for Michelle Obama NYC bash",
      "sourceUrl": "http://articles.nydailynews.com/2012-03-20/news/31212051_1_first-lady-starry-crowd-dynamic-duo"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 15
    },
    {
      "parentId": 15,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "He's pretty liberal, at least in terms of the animal rights issue. Stiller joined a slew of celebrities pals in a public service announcement designed to raise awareness about the killing of dolphins off the coast of Japan.",
      "sourceTitle": "Hollywood and \"The Cove\" Join Forces for Dolphin Awareness PSA",
      "sourceUrl": "http://mashable.com/2010/04/22/the-cove-psa/"
    }
  ],
